Class BorrowController

  • java.lang.Object
    • library.BorrowController

  • public class BorrowController
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a controller for the borrow funkction. It test first if its possible for user to borrow and if its true, then it proceeds to make the borrow. there is a search here for media, it uses the keys to identify them and puts them on display.
